        <abstract> 
<p>Glad to hear the news about the professorship was partly erroneous, but still wishes JVC to have the rights to translate [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>]. Has written to Herr Koch [of Schweizerbart], but not in such a way as to commit JVC to publish with him.</p> 
        </abstract>
